.TH FTPSYNC-CRON 1 "2026-03-27" "ctxos-core 1.0.0" "CTX OS Manual"
.SH NAME
ftpsync-cron \- cron wrapper for ftpsync with locking and retries
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ftpsync-cron
.SH DESCRIPTION
Silent cron-friendly wrapper around ftpsync. Uses flock to prevent overlapping
runs, retries on failure, and logs to /var/log/ctxos-ftpsync.log.
.SH CONFIGURATION
Reads /etc/ctxos/ftpsync.conf if present.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ftpsync (1)
